  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can You Escape in Time? </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Door is an escape room experience that plunges you into a series of immersive, unsettling environments, each with its own unique story and chilling challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make it to the exit either alone or with friends – the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a trap-filled lair built by a mad scientist, to a haunted doll's room cursed by the spirit of a dead child, and a secret laboratory where hallucinations blur reality, every episode delivers a fresh and thrilling mystery!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More Than Meets the Eye</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Door offers five distinct episodes, each with a new theme, story, and puzzle mechanics. Players can select episodes as if choosing books from a library, ensuring that no two adventures feel the same.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Ultimate Test</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether facing the unknown alone or with friends, Another Door delivers an unforgettable VR adventure filled with suspense, teamwork, and intricate puzzles that will push your mind to its limits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Find hidden collectibles scattered</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Experience five unique themes with their own puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Escape before it’s too late</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Immersive audio design</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Online co-op</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can You Escape in Time? </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/d2d653a477fdb5fbb043582c8901c897.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Door is an escape room experience that plunges you into a series of immersive, unsettling environments, each with its own unique story and chilling challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make it to the exit either alone or with friends – the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a trap-filled lair built by a mad scientist, to a haunted doll's room cursed by the spirit of a dead child, and a secret laboratory where hallucinations blur reality, every episode delivers a fresh and thrilling mystery!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More Than Meets the Eye</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/79f6356201a68ccb82676b797e0e76f2.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Door offers five distinct episodes, each with a new theme, story, and puzzle mechanics. Players can select episodes as if choosing books from a library, ensuring that no two adventures feel the same.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Ultimate Test</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.poster.avif?t=1737697230\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.webm?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/573822a9ebfdfeecb594b825b049f319.mp4?t=1737697230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether facing the unknown alone or with friends, Another Door delivers an unforgettable VR adventure filled with suspense, teamwork, and intricate puzzles that will push your mind to its limits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Find hidden collectibles scattered</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Experience five unique themes with their own puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Escape before it’s too late</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Immersive audio design</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Online co-op</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
